Exploration enrichment pathways with differentially expressed (DE) genes between old versus young

Team Le Grand

02 mai,2022

Pathway explored : REACTOME GENE AND PROTEIN EXPRESSION BY JAK STAT SIGNALING AFTER INTERLEUKIN 12 STIMULATION

This pathway contain 38 genes.

In these 38 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes DE significant with a major participation in the enrichment (leadingEdge cal by fgsea filter by padj<0.05).
